---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Riya Hariyaplar</title>

    <!-- prevent Google indexing -->
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f8fafc;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --text: #0f172a;
        --muted: #475569;
        --accent: #2563eb;
        --accent-light: #dbeafe;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, #f1f5f9);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .container {
        width: min(1000px, 90%);
        margin: auto;
      }

      nav {
        padding: 1rem 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        margin-left: 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }

      .avatar {
        width: 170px;
        height: 170px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border: 3px solid #2563eb;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .subtitle {
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .intro {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 700px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .buttons {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        margin: 0.5rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: white;
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        color: var(--accent);
        background: var(--accent-light);
      }

      section {
        margin-top: 4rem;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .education, .contact {
        background: var(--card);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }

      ul {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="container">
      <div><strong>Riya Hariyaplar</strong></div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#education">Education</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <img class="avatar" src="/headshotpic.jpg" alt="Riya Hariyaplar headshot" />

        <h1>Riya Hariyaplar</h1>

        <div class="subtitle">
          UCLA student studying Economics with a focus on Data Science
        </div>

        <div class="intro">
          I approach problems through an economic lens, using data to understand behavior, uncover patterns, and drive informed decision-making. At UCLA, I’ve built a strong foundation in quantitative analysis, combining statistical methods with economic theory to explore real-world challenges. I’m particularly interested in applying data-driven insights to areas like market dynamics, product strategy, and policy, where analytical thinking can translate into tangible impact.
        </div>

        <div class="buttons">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/resume">Resume</a>

          <a
            class="btn btn-secondary"
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/riyahariyaplar/"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M6.94 8.5A1.56 1.56 0 1 1 6.94 5.4a1.56 1.56 0 0 1 0 3.1ZM5.59 9.74h2.7V18h-2.7V9.74Zm4.37 0h2.59v1.13h.04c.36-.68 1.24-1.4 2.55-1.4 2.72 0 3.22 1.79 3.22 4.11V18h-2.7v-3.92c0-.94-.02-2.15-1.31-2.15-1.31 0-1.51 1.02-1.51 2.08V18h-2.7V9.74Z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="education">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="education">
          <strong>University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA)</strong><br />
          B.S. in Economics & Data Science Double Major<br />
          Graduation: June 2026<br />
          GPA: 3.9

          <ul>
            <li>
              Affiliations: Tech & Finance Crew of Bruin Women in Business,
              Bruin Capital Management, AI Club, Disabled Student Union
            </li>
            <li>
              Relevant Coursework: Corporate Strategy, Advanced Data Science,
              Multivariable Calculus, Data Structures and Design, Discrete Math,
              Advanced Probability & Statistics, Machine Learning,
              Microeconomic Theory, Accounting
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <div class="contact">
          <p>
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:riya.hariyaplar@gmail.com">
              riya.hariyaplar@gmail.com
            </a>
          </p>

          <p>
            Phone:
            <a href="tel:4088875180">408-887-5180</a>
          </p>

          <p>Location: San Jose, CA</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      2026 Riya Hariyaplar. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
